additionalProperty.name: Ingredients
additionalProperty.value: Active Constituents: 9.75g/kg Pyrethrins 29.89g/kg N-Octyl Bicycloheptene Dicarboximide 15.6g/kg Piperonyl Butoxide

additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: KEEP OUT OF REACH OF CHILDREN. EXTREMELY FLAMMABLE. Do not direct onto humans, pets, exposed food, water, food preparation areas or food utensils. Do not allow children & pets to play or eat directly under device. Do not use in outdoor areas that are completely enclosed by walls or screens, e.g. sunrooms. Do not operate near eyes or towards the face. Excessive inhalation or exposure may cause allergy in sensitive individuals. Avoid inhalation of spray mist. DO NOT STORE OR USE NEAR FIRE OR FLAME. DO NOT SMOKE DURING USE. VERY ECOTOXIC TO AQUATIC LIFE. DO NOT THROW PRODUCT INTO WATERWAYS.
